Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope he'll get used to the stables.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:07.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine. He's a calm one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:11.11,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, because one \Nwild horse is enough to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.32,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:18.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.74,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but can you \Nplease not butt in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.48,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You did the same thing during our audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.82,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.32,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We're pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.90,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, you should be thanking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're pros?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.09,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.29,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Though, we're missing a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.04,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.25,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We even have a hit song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:37.26,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess you youngins haven't \Nheard of the Condor Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.58,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We were even on a commercial once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Condor Queens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now a tune to make men merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co-Co-Co-Condor! Co-Co-Co-Condor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.70,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cut that out?\N You're embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.25,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,These days, we're mostly touring the \Ncountry playing some modest live shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.89,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say music isn't so much a job anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The Condor Queens?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.55,Default,Gramp,0000,0000,0000,,This is your grandpappy's theme song!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:22.80,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 4 \N Getting Angry and Dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.02,Default,book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Vocal Training
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.23,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.85,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.79,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Follow that bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.18,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.24,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker! Stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I've been your fan since I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:29.02,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That gives me an idea! \NWould you play at the World Music Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't they be just perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.39,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,They sure would!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:36.17,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean you \Nwithdraw your audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.04,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that, Konatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.84,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! We can't beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.72,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great, if you'd take us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.66,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,We try to not be picky about our venues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.56,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:53.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you put them up \Nat your place until the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.20,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're short on rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa lives in a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.35,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.81,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We're no Buddhas;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've got no business \Nstaying at a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.19,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We've got enough cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our own trusty abode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.28,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Unless your temple has \Na nice, big parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.59,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just told me from
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the start that you knew my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:22.21,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just couldn't contain myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.56,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.27,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.47,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.17,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Is there choir practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:32.93,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.48,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:39.19,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to Okita's house\Nwith some band, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.99,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What a great spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.54,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since \Nwe could kick back like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:50.09,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, Japan's too cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.13,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:55.58,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, you're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.50,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.52,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.55,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.18,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have enough \Ntime to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you sleep in their camper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:17.67,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.52,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.90,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.71,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,I found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.91,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,I found Mahiru's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.90,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Will you look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.05,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Come, sit down, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.99,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I can't stay long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:44.42,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We met Mahiru back when we were on tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.51,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,We wrote a song together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.37,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,"Amigo, Amigo."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:52.87,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. That was \Nour one-hit wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.12,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Saying we wrote that \Nsong isn't quite right;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's more like it was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.89,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiru never mentioned it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:02.13,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.51,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:08.53,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we considered her a \Ndear friend and benefactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might even say we \Nwere in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.45,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not your daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.33,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.23,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,No dirty jokes around the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.67,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,You look a lot like she did back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.69,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But she was more cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.40,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,And her hair was a touch longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.50,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like only yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:45.37,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe \Nthat Mahiru's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.41,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Feel like galloping, Sabure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.31,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want my Poem gettin' spooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.31,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.39,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Poem, he'll eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.56,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.04,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you \Nabout today's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.59,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're having it at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:13.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I was wondering if \Nit's okay if I skip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.37,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.94,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The guys said they're going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a test run at the beach house stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it might be good \Nto watch the pros at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.33,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Why don't we all \Nskip, and check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.43,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.81,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't made any progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.94,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a game to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who I'm riding with, \Nor how much I respect them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we ride together, \NI want to be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.74,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You need to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.46,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If all you want is to be in a fan club,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm quitting the choir club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.57,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.27,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.07,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Is that falsetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.57,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.68,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.48,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We should leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.13,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,A pro should never be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.09,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.31,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like us to give \Nyou our slot on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.10,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,You're a senior, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.62,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep on singing \Nlong after graduation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.57,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,but it won't be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.47,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a song you can only sing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the people and feelings you've got now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.96,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like our spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.91,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:08.81,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.25,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You think graduation's a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to graduate from life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:22.71,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,We're not old enough to \Ngive up the things we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:27.26,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go back to \Nyour own stage, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.78,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.54,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:45.63,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.80,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa's not home, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.66,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:56.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a stage left \Nthat we could sing on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.99,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Was that falsetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Falsetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.29,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.90,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Miyamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:45.26,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Without her, all we can do are sit-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:51.98,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. \NSakai's in this club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.68,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And she used to be \Nin the music school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:58.27,Default,book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Vocal Training
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:58.11,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've never actually heard her sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.55,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking a supplementary class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.94,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Should I invite her next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.77,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.00,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.51,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.61,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.21,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.54,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,...too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.21,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.32,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.52,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's one place that hasn't \Nfound a performer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.18,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.21,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they'll use \Nyou, but it's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:39.52,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.02,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.78,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:53.78,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Have you chosen a performer \Nfor the World Music Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.05,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.13,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She said she knew someone who might be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,interested, and would introduce us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.52,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I think she might still be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.88,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.88,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sakai Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.73,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.16,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.28,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I'm just glad you found a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.23,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I haven't ran that hard in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you found an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If only I was a virtuoso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I bet by now I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.20,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.21,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it. I can't sing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.58,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:52.97,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,When you said you quit \Nmusic, did you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.52,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no virtuoso, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.44,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.40,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san, do you know \Nanything about this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? I'm not all that familiar with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.13,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.23,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's really pretty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.55,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.77,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.49,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto never showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:11.14,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I want you guys to listen to the \NCD and practice your parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.79,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We need to maximize our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.39,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.88,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a consolation prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's win the popularity vote \Nand sing on the main stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.45,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.45,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.12,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.75,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not one match...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lasso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.90,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give our best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Together, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:32.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The waves break on the \Nshore. The waves retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My thoughts ride...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:40.22,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the surf. In the distance, I see a white...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:44.85,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...beach. Under the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...hot sun, aloha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.91,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.98,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu, is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.45,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is far from us, \Nso nobody's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.47,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,At least there's the consolation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.35,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's really into their show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.77,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This is the song that your \Nmom helped compose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.83,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.31,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.55,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.58,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wait for an audience to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.67,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You sing to {\i1}make{\i0} the audience come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:16.38,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Want us to go out with \Nyou for an encore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:18.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That stage is ours, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.29,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.90,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.46,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:35.98,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.30,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.57,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.85,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you gave up music.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.56,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.62,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Whether healthy or sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.13,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether happy or sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to write songs that always fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.34,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, we didn't understand what she meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and laughed it off as some crazy dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.19,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe she was talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.44,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.92,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you do or don't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.67,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,Music is a constant companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.03,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Even your heartbeat is music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:27.12,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That's what your mother \Ntold us, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.22,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You can't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.11,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:38.96,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That's a letter we got from your \Nmother when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.36,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should talk sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.72,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There really is nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Not true. We've got three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.78,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You better sing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.98,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is so not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.39,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.20,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The waves break on the shore. The waves retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:21.58,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My thoughts ride the surf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:28.43,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the distance, I see a white beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:33.22,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Under the hot sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.02,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}aloha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.69,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have your picture, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:45.57,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Nothin's gonna steal my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.71,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:51.08,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:31.05,Default,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congratulations On Your Win! \NShirohamazaka High's Tanaka Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I got cake for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.02,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:34.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Horses for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.04,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.91,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 5 \NThrowing Away and Holding On
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:39.94,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about \Ngetting rid of the piano in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
